Matrix from hell - compatibility issues

Containers : 
    - docker utilizes lxc containers

Containers vs Virtual machines : 
    - Containers will share the OS
    - virtual machine will have its own OS
    - Containers sit inside VM in big apps
    - So containers and VMs work together
